[normal]9
[normal] [bold]              [bold]Manchester Gold Mentoring Scheme: [bold]Students are matched on a one to one basis with an experienced member of staff (a mentor) and will be
[normal] in contact with them over a nine month period. The programme aims to help students with career planning and decision making about their future options
[normal].
